caption.title: Serum lipid levels in rats.
caption.p: ( A) Cholesterol. ( B) TG. C, Casein; T, tofu; S, soy oil; F, fish oil. Values are means ± SD, n = 7–8. Results of statistical analyses are presented in S1 Appendix. Results of the post hoc analysis and 95% family-wise confidence levels are also shown. Results of statistical analyses are presented in S1 Appendix.
